"method to try out :func:`~flask.url_for`. "
":meth:`~flask.Flask.test_request_context` tells Flask to behave as though"
" it's handling a request even while we use a Python shell. See :ref"
":`context-locals`."
msgstr ""
"Por ejemplo, aquí usamos el método "
":meth:`~flask.Flask.test_request_context` para probar "
":func:`~flask.url_for`. :meth:`~flask.Flask.test_request_context` le dice"
" a Flask que se comporte como si estuviera manejando una petición incluso"
" mientras usamos un shell de Python. Ver :ref:`context-locals`."

#: ../../quickstart.rst:356
msgid "HTTP Methods"
msgstr "Métodos HTTP"

